However, in your setup where the adversary gets control of both the key 
and the entire ciphertext, a constant time-space solution exists by 
inverting AES-GCM auth tags.The initialization block can be computed as 
generating the authentication input, XOR with the observed tag, then 
decrypt using AES-ECB, then we can work forward to decrypt the rest of 
the data as normal.

